@{fg shine}ENGLISH @{"DEUTSCH" link DEUTSCH}@{fg text}

@{b}WELCOME!@{ub}

  Congratulations for  choosing  microgolded!  microgolded  is  a
  simple yet powerful editor for AmigaOS and MorphOS.

@{b}ABOUT MICROGOLDED@{ub}

  microgolded is a single-file variant of the GoldED  Studio  AIX
  editor. It does not require installation, an assign or a folder
  with catalogs, custom libraries, fonts  and  images.  It  is  a
  single  file designed to be placed in the system's c folder. It
  does not include features targeted at  software  developers  or
  web  site  designers  but  has  all  features needed for simple
  editing tasks such as changing the  startup-sequence.  It  will
  run on a partially installed system without startup-sequence.

@{b}INSTALLATION@{ub}

  This product does  not  require  installation.  Just  drag  the
  executable to the preferred place (such as the c folder on your
  boot disk).

@{b}OPTIONAL FILES@{ub}

  The  folder  [schemes]  contains  optional  color  and   widget
  schemes.  You  can  load a color scheme into the editor via the
  editor's display dialog: click on the  OPEN  button  below  the
  USER INTERFACE list.

@{b}HARDWARE REQUIREMENTS@{ub}

  This product requires AmigaOS3.5/68020+ and 2 MB  free  RAM  as
  minimum  system. However, without a graphics card and without a
  fast CPU, you will not be able to enjoy this  software.  It  is
  hightly recommended to install a graphics card and to run it at
  least on a 060/40 CPU or to run the software on a PC  with  UAE
  or to use it with MorphOS on a Pegasos PPC computer.

@{b}PURCHASING@{ub}

  Using microgolded is free for a 30 days trial  period.  If  you
  want  to continue using it beyond the free trial period, please
  visit our online shop and purchase microgolded.

  http://golded.dietmar-eilert.de

